<li><span class="nowrap">1990: <a href="/wiki/Ivan_Dziuba" title="Ivan Dziuba">Ivan Dziuba</a> / <a href="/wiki/Valeriy_Shevchuk" title="Valeriy Shevchuk">Valeriy Shevchuk</a></span></li>
